message.content:
Case Based. 

Explanation: The paper focuses on the use of Case-Based Reasoning (CBR) as a form of "caching" solved problems to speed up later problem solving. The paper discusses the utility problem associated with caching cases and the construction of a cost model to predict the effect of changes to the case memory. These are all related to the use of CBR. There is no mention of any other sub-category of AI in the text.
